 <h1>Rock Breaker</h1>
 <h3>Source</h3>
 <text pwt="true"><style color="0xaaaaaa" italic="true" pwt="true">Note: this page is ported from MCMOD's GTCEu wiki.<br/>Author: <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/285765/">TBS</style>, <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/179043/">花海</style>, <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/119280/">Oganesson897</style>, <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/482827/">存档是希望</style>, <style color="0xa4e7ff" hover-info="url" pwt="true" underlined="true" url-link="https://center.mcmod.cn/2/">重生是希望</style><br/></style></text>
 <h2 font-color="0xff0000">WARNING!!!</h2>
 <text isCenter="true">
  <style color="0xff0000" pwt="true">The warning means this is not a reliable page.</style>
